<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="breeze-n">breeze <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /briːz/    美 /briːz/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>微风；轻风；轻而易举的事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>flowers waving in the breeze 
在微风中摇曳的花朵</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Studying <strong>was a breeze</strong> for Nigel. 
对于尼格尔来说学习是小菜一碟。</p><footer>2008 江西</footer></div></div>